data.description: Introducing a stunning 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home that combines elegance with comfort. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this property boasts a spacious interior with high ceilings, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere.  Step inside and be greeted by a warm and inviting living space, highlighted by a wood-burning fireplace that serves as the heart of the home. This cozy feature is perfect for those chilly evenings, creating a perfect spot for relaxation and gatherings with family and friends.  The generously-sized bedrooms provide ample space for rest and relaxation, with plenty of natural light flowing through large windows. The master suite offers a private oasis with an en-suite bath, ensuring comfort and convenience.  Entertainment enthusiasts will appreciate the full basement, complete with a bar and pool table. Whether it's game nights or hosting friends, this space is perfect for creating lasting memories.
